abstract: New York Giants defensive end Justin Tuck may be ready to return to field after several weeks of dealing with neck and groin injuries.
snippet: After dealing with neck and groin injuries for several weeks, defensive end Justin Tuck may be back in action on Sunday.
lead_paragraph: After dealing with neck and groin injuries for several weeks, defensive end Justin Tuck may be back in action on Sunday.

headline.main: Giants Hope Tuck’s Cheerleading Days Are Over
